translated_string:
// init $25, $4f
No! I am not the grandson of that cold-blooded animal! Where was he when I was working so hard to survive? He gave me this life, didn't he? And when he was in need, he remembered that there was a person like me! Isn't that selfish at all?

// init $03, $34
Brother... I remember my brother once told me to tolerate the mistakes of others. A life of regret is the most miserable.

translated_string:
// init $00, $00
To my son whose name I don't know yet: I'm sorry I don't think I'll see you anymore... My love ~ life is full of hopelessness, starting from the moment I met your father. Even though it was a tragedy, the fruit of my heart is still sweet. Resentment? Sadness? Sadness? My unknown son, my love, must not be so, for one must always learn to understand. I'm going to disappear, my love, and I hope you'll understand my feelings too... even though you may not see it... I'm sorry... I don't think I'll see you anymore... my love... my unknown son... Sonice's absolute words...

original_string:
昱日
加爾企業舉行了
盛大的董可交接
儀式。
妮娜為此，還頻
頻的在會場中落淚。
儀式很順利的舉
行完畢了。
加爾企業，由新
一代的董事~
馬克接任。
新聞、報紙上滿
滿的都是馬克就
職的消息。
translated_string: Rene Garr Enterprises held a grand handover ceremony. Nina shed tears frequently in the meeting for this purpose. The ceremony went smoothly. Gale Enterprises, the new generation of directors ~ Mark to take over. The news and newspapers were full of news of Mark's inauguration.
